{"orig":"/Users/kalaverin/src/lang/nim/lib/pure/marshal.nim","nimble":"stdlib","moduleDescription":"<p>This module contains procs for <span id=\"serialization_1\">serialization</span> and <span id=\"deserialization_1\">deserialization</span> of arbitrary Nim data structures. The serialization format uses <span id=\"json_1\">JSON</span>.</p>\n<p><strong>Restriction:</strong> For objects, their type is <strong>not</strong> serialized. This means essentially that it does not work if the object has some other runtime type than its compiletime type.</p>\n\n<h1><a class=\"toc-backref\" id=\"basic-usage\" href=\"#basic-usage\">Basic usage</a></h1><strong>Note:</strong> The <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">to</span></span></tt> and <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Operator\">$$</span></span></tt> operations are available at compile-time!\n<h1><a class=\"toc-backref\" id=\"see-also\" href=\"#see-also\">See also</a></h1><ul class=\"simple\"><li><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"streams.html\">streams module</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference external\" href=\"json.html\">json module</a></li>\n</ul>\n","entries":[{"name":"load","type":"skProc","line":282,"col":0,"code":"proc load[T](s: Stream; data: var T)","signature":{"arguments":[{"name":"s","type":"Stream"},{"name":"data","type":"var T"}],"genericParams":[{"name":"T"}]},"description":"Loads <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">data</span></span></tt> from the stream <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">s</span></span></tt>. Raises <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">IOError</span></span></tt> in case of an error."},{"name":"store","type":"skProc","line":295,"col":0,"code":"proc store[T](s: Stream; data: sink T)","signature":{"arguments":[{"name":"s","type":"Stream"},{"name":"data","type":"sink T"}],"genericParams":[{"name":"T"}]},"description":"Stores <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">data</span></span></tt> into the stream <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">s</span></span></tt>. Raises <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">IOError</span></span></tt> in case of an error."},{"name":"`$$`","type":"skProc","line":317,"col":0,"code":"proc `$$`[T](x: sink T): string","signature":{"return":"string","arguments":[{"name":"x","type":"sink T"}],"genericParams":[{"name":"T"}]},"description":"<p>Returns a string representation of <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">x</span></span></tt> (serialization, marshalling).</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> to serialize <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">x</span></span></tt> to JSON use <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Operator\">%</span><span class=\"Identifier\">x</span></span></tt> from the <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">json</span></span></tt> module or <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">jsonutils</span><span class=\"Operator\">.</span><span class=\"Identifier\">toJson</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"Identifier\">x</span><span class=\"Punctuation\">)</span></span></tt>.</p>\n"},{"name":"to","type":"skProc","line":348,"col":0,"code":"proc to[T](data: string): T","signature":{"return":"T","arguments":[{"name":"data","type":"string"}],"genericParams":[{"name":"T"}]},"description":"Reads data and transforms it to a type <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\"><span class=\"Identifier\">T</span></span></tt> (deserialization, unmarshalling)."}]}